# Subagent Prompts (copy-paste into chat)

Use these as virtual subagents by pasting the role or command below into Cursor chat.

## Roles

1. **UI Architect**  
   Act as UI Architect. Build/modify only design system and layout components.

2. **Section Engineer**  
   Act as Section Engineer. Implement section using only data files and reusable components.

3. **Chat API Engineer**  
   Act as Chat API Engineer. Work only on /app/api/chat + lib, with strict validation and guardrails.

4. **QA Auditor**  
   Act as QA Auditor. Run checks, find regressions, and give exact fixes.

---

## Commands you can paste

**Generic (follow rules, plan first):**  
Follow all active rules. Before coding: plan + files + deps. Then implement.

**Section Engineer (Work section):**  
Act as Section Engineer. Add/modify Work section from data/projects.ts only. Render only status === "published". Keep existing UI style. After coding run lint + type-check and report.

**Chat API Engineer (route + guardrails):**  
Act as Chat API Engineer. Implement app/api/chat/route.ts with: zod input validation, basic rate limiting, server-side Anthropic key usage only, answers only from me/projects/skills data. After coding run lint + type-check and report.

**QA Auditor (a11y, responsive, perf):**  
Act as QA Auditor. Check accessibility, mobile responsiveness, and animation performance. List issues by severity with file paths and exact fixes.
